N2  - Merger behavior is explored within the framework of the desire to manage resources and market dependencies. It is argued that market power resides in the bilateral relationships between buyer and seller, and that these dependencies influence merger strategy. Results of the study indicate that there is such a relationship between merger strategy and relative market power.
